* Caroline De Vita – design
* Lance Ellison – piano, vocals
* D.A. Fleischer – photography
* Jane Higgins – design
* Rick and Bubba – vocals
* Jack Skinner – mastering
* Shawn Smith – background vocals, vocals
* Ross Ian Stein – engineer, producer
* Shecky Stein – piano

